controlled|db/lane/rewind.rs|rewind_lane|lane_rewind_projection|RestoreProjection|run_ref_advancing_projection|apply_rewind_workdir_projection,sync_lane_workdir
controlled|db/lane/workdir/record.rs|record_lane_workdir_locked|observed_lane_checkpoint|ObservedCheckpoint|run_ref_advancing_projection|build_root_for_selected_disk_files_incremental,complete_workspace_checkpoint
